GONNA MAKE ME UNPLUG MY CHILD.

00:15.448 --> 00:17.183
I'LL BE REPRESENTING
MS. YOUNG.

00:17.183 --> 00:18.519
SHE'S NOT
EVEN A LAWYER.

00:18.519 --> 00:20.821
SHE'S NOT A LAWYER,
BUT SHE HAS A POINT.

00:20.821 --> 00:22.689
BUT I'D LOVE
TO SEE YOU AGAIN.

00:22.689 --> 00:24.324
I'D LIKE THAT.

00:24.324 --> 00:25.959
I HAVE IT.

00:25.959 --> 00:30.363
NOW, YOU WILL DO WHAT I SAY,
OR I WILL TURN YOUR ASS IN.

00:32.866 --> 00:34.635
WHY ARE YOU
SO QUIET NOW?

00:36.503 --> 00:38.639
YOU HAD MY CAR?

00:38.639 --> 00:40.541
YES.

00:40.541 --> 00:42.809
WHY?

00:42.809 --> 00:45.378
HMM. INSURANCE.

00:45.378 --> 00:47.047
WHY WOULD YOU NEED
INSURANCE?

00:47.047 --> 00:49.382
WHY DOES ANYONE
NEED INSURANCE, JEFFERY?

00:49.382 --> 00:51.785
TO COVER YOU
IN THE EVENT OF AN INCIDENT.

00:51.785 --> 00:53.554
OR IN THIS CASE,
TO COVER ME

00:53.554 --> 00:57.357
IN THE EVENT OF YOU NOT DOING
WHAT I'M ASKING YOU TO DO.

00:57.357 --> 01:00.293
HAVE YOU HAD IT
THIS WHOLE TIME?

01:00.293 --> 01:02.035
YES.

01:02.035 --> 01:03.604
WHERE IS IT?

01:04.738 --> 01:06.940
SAFE...FOR NOW.

01:08.708 --> 01:10.443
WHAT ARE YOU
GONNA DO WITH IT?

01:10.443 --> 01:12.546
WELL, NOW, THAT DEPENDS.

01:13.514 --> 01:15.481
ON?

01:15.481 --> 01:17.818
ON WHAT
YOU'RE GOING TO DO.

01:17.818 --> 01:20.020
WHAT'S ‐‐ WHAT IS THAT?

01:20.020 --> 01:22.055
WELL, LET'S SEE.

01:22.055 --> 01:24.525
FIRST OF ALL,
YOU WILL LISTEN TO ME,

01:24.525 --> 01:26.527
AND YOU WILL LISTEN
CLOSELY.

01:26.527 --> 01:29.429
NOW, I DON'T KNOW WHO
YOU THINK YOU HAVE BECOME,

01:29.429 --> 01:31.364
BUT THIS LAVENDER
WILL NOT DO

01:31.364 --> 01:34.601
FOR THE IMAGE THAT I HAVE SET
FOR THIS FAMILY.

01:34.601 --> 01:38.639
YOU WILL GET INTO LINE, AND YOU
WILL GET INTO LINE QUICKLY.

01:38.639 --> 01:41.608
NOW, YOU WILL PICK UP YOUR KEYS
TO THE APARTMENT.

01:41.608 --> 01:43.343
YOU WILL CALL
THE TAILOR,

01:43.343 --> 01:45.546
AND YOU WILL HAVE
SOME SUITS MADE ‐‐

01:45.546 --> 01:50.016
SIMPLE, BLACK, BLUES, GRAYS.

01:50.016 --> 01:52.052
YOUR PHONE
WILL BE TURNED ON,

01:52.052 --> 01:54.688
AND YOUR CREDIT CARDS
WILL BE REINSTATED,

01:54.688 --> 01:57.558
AND YOU WILL RESUME YOUR JOB
AT THE FACILITY.

01:57.558 --> 02:00.393
YOUR LIFE WILL RETURN
TO THE WAY IT HAD BEEN

02:00.393 --> 02:03.970
BEFORE THIS NEWFOUND
FOOLISHNESS.

02:03.970 --> 02:06.406
EXCEPT THIS TIME WITH A WOMAN.
MOM, I ‐‐

02:06.406 --> 02:08.408
THAT'S WHAT YOU
ARE GOING TO DO, JEFFERY.

02:08.408 --> 02:11.745
MOM, I WASN'T HAPPY
IN THAT LIFE.

02:11.745 --> 02:15.716
JEFFERY, I DON'T KNOW WHY NOT.
IT'S YOUR LIFE.

02:15.716 --> 02:17.483
IT'S YOUR LIFE, MOM,
NOT MINE.

02:17.483 --> 02:20.120
YOUR LIFE, MY LIFE.
ONE AND THE SAME.

02:20.120 --> 02:22.455
[ SIGHS ]
NO, IT'S NOT, MOM.

02:22.455 --> 02:23.924
IT'S NOT THE SAME.

02:23.924 --> 02:26.860
I KNOW YOU THINK
YOU WANT THAT LIFE,

02:26.860 --> 02:28.795
BUT THERE'S ANOTHER LIFE.

02:28.795 --> 02:30.564
LIFE IN PRISON.

02:30.564 --> 02:32.999
I'M YOUR SON.

02:32.999 --> 02:35.335
YES.

02:35.335 --> 02:38.004
YOU ARE MY SON.

02:40.206 --> 02:43.409
AND BECAUSE YOU ARE MY SON,
YOU WILL DO AS I SAY.

02:48.582 --> 02:51.417
AND IF I REFUSE?

02:51.417 --> 02:54.755
THEN YOU GO TO PRISON.

02:56.089 --> 02:58.224
I‐I DIDN'T HAVE ANYTHING
TO DO WITH THIS.

02:58.224 --> 03:00.466
I DON'T KNOW THAT.

03:00.466 --> 03:03.169
OH, MOM.

03:03.169 --> 03:05.438
AND NEITHER
WILL THE POLICE.

03:11.111 --> 03:13.013
YOU WOULD DO THAT TO ME?

03:13.013 --> 03:17.483
AS FAST AS YOU CAN SAY
"I'M A BAD BITCH."

03:20.654 --> 03:22.856
I‐I DON'T KNOW
WHAT THE PROBLEM IS, JEFFERY.

03:22.856 --> 03:24.024
YOU HAVE A GREAT LIFE.

03:28.161 --> 03:30.130
IT'S ‐‐
IT'S NOT WHO I AM, MOM.

03:30.130 --> 03:31.331
YES, IT IS WHO YOU ARE.
NO.

03:31.331 --> 03:34.701
NO. NO, IT'S NOT.

03:34.701 --> 03:37.137
JEFFERY, YOU ARE
WHO I CREATED YOU TO BE.

03:37.137 --> 03:41.542
THAT'S WHAT IT'S LIKE WHEN
YOU'RE BORN INTO MEANS.

03:41.542 --> 03:45.812
YOU'RE BORN INTO A LIFESTYLE,
INTO AN IMAGE, EXPECTATIONS.

03:45.812 --> 03:47.814
IT'S LIKE ROYALTY.

03:51.518 --> 03:54.120
YOUR LIFE
DOESN'T BELONG TO YOU.

03:54.120 --> 03:56.089
IT BELONGS TO THE MONARCH.

03:56.089 --> 03:58.925
THAT'S HOW IT IS.
DO YOU UNDERSTAND?

03:58.925 --> 04:02.736
WE ARE NOT ROYALTY, MOM.

04:02.736 --> 04:06.039
AND YOU ARE NOT A QUEEN.

04:07.608 --> 04:09.109
WOW.

04:11.244 --> 04:13.514
I CAN'T BELIEVE YOU.

04:13.514 --> 04:15.582
JEFFERY,
YOU WANT TO PLAY GROWN‐UP?

04:15.582 --> 04:17.584
WELL, THIS IS
HOW GROWN‐UPS REACT.

04:17.584 --> 04:19.786
FOR EVERY ACTION,
THERE IS A REACTION.

04:19.786 --> 04:21.588
NOW, YOUR FATHER
AND MR. CRYER

04:21.588 --> 04:23.924
ARE MAKING AN ANNOUNCEMENT
IN A FEW DAYS,

04:23.924 --> 04:26.660
AND YOU WILL SHOW UP THERE
DRESSED IN A BLACK SUIT

04:26.660 --> 04:28.862
WITH A GIRL FROM YOUR...

04:32.699 --> 04:36.302
I WILL TAKE YOUR SILENCE
AS COMPLIANCE.

04:38.938 --> 04:41.274
NOW LEAVE THIS PLACE

04:41.274 --> 04:46.747
AND NEVER, EVER MEET ME
DRESSED THAT WAY AGAIN.

04:51.618 --> 04:53.419
YES.

04:53.419 --> 04:55.656
AND, JEFFERY?

04:55.656 --> 04:57.090
YEAH?

04:57.090 --> 04:58.592
"YEAH"?

04:59.826 --> 05:02.302
YES, MOM.

05:02.302 --> 05:04.971
YOU TELL THAT GIRL

05:04.971 --> 05:08.942
THAT I WILL SHOW HER
WHAT A BAD BITCH REALLY IS.

05:11.311 --> 05:13.814
LOVE YOU, SON.

