HI.

05:52.519 --> 05:54.020
[ MONITOR BEEPING ]
HOW ARE YOU?

05:54.020 --> 05:57.791
STILL WAITING ON GOD.

05:57.791 --> 05:59.993
[ VENTILATOR HISSING ]

05:59.993 --> 06:01.467
ANY CHANGE?

06:03.570 --> 06:05.471
NO.

06:05.471 --> 06:08.041
I'M SORRY.

06:08.041 --> 06:10.911
IT'S FINE.

06:10.911 --> 06:12.713
HOW LONG YOU BEEN HERE, HANNA?
ALL NIGHT?

06:12.713 --> 06:15.281
NO. NOT THIS TIME.

06:15.281 --> 06:17.751
I HAVE SPENT THE NIGHT
OUT THERE IN THE WAITING ROOM,

06:17.751 --> 06:23.056
BUT I...I'VE JUST BEEN HERE
SEVERAL HOURS TODAY.

06:23.056 --> 06:25.892
THEY MAKE ME LEAVE AFTER
VISITING HOURS ARE OVER.

06:25.892 --> 06:27.861
THIS IS NOT GOOD, HANNA.

06:27.861 --> 06:31.231
I FEEL LIKE
HE KNOWS I'M HERE.

06:31.231 --> 06:33.834
I KNOW HE KNOWS I'M HERE.

06:33.834 --> 06:35.268
AND WOULD HE WANT THAT?

06:35.268 --> 06:38.672
YOU SITTING HERE WORRIED OVER
HIM ALL NIGHT, NOT EATING?

06:38.672 --> 06:40.406
[ CHUCKLES ]

06:40.406 --> 06:42.776
NO, HE WOULD NOT
WANT THAT.

06:42.776 --> 06:44.845
[ BEEPING AND HISSING CONTINUE ]

06:44.845 --> 06:47.914
I CAN HEAR HIM
SAYING IT NOW.

06:47.914 --> 06:52.385
"MAMA, GET UP AND GO SOMEWHERE
AND EAT SOMETHING."

06:52.385 --> 06:54.020
[ CHUCKLES ]
SMART KID.

06:55.756 --> 06:57.390
MAYBE YOU
SHOULD LISTEN TO HIM.

06:57.390 --> 07:00.100
I WANT TO BE HERE
WHEN HE WAKES UP.

07:02.068 --> 07:04.805
I WANT TO SEE THE MIRACLE.

07:04.805 --> 07:07.107
HANNA...

07:07.107 --> 07:09.309
[ SCOFFS ] COME ON.
LISTEN TO YOUR BOY.

07:09.309 --> 07:11.712
NO.

07:11.712 --> 07:13.413
HANNA, WE'LL BE RIGHT DOWN
THE HALL IN THE CAFETERIA.

07:13.413 --> 07:15.048
I CAN'T EAT THAT FOOD.

07:15.048 --> 07:17.483
THERE MUST BE SOMETHING
ON THE MENU YOU CAN EAT.

07:17.483 --> 07:18.619
COME ON.

07:20.086 --> 07:22.823
COME ON. LET'S GO DOWN
TO THE CAFETERIA.

07:22.823 --> 07:24.758
I'M FINE.

07:26.192 --> 07:27.761
COME ON.

07:27.761 --> 07:29.129
ARE YOU ALWAYS
THIS PERSISTENT?

07:29.129 --> 07:31.331
YES, I AM.
NOW COME ON.

07:31.331 --> 07:34.467
ALL RIGHT, 'CAUSE YOU
ARE NOT GONNA GIVE UP,

07:34.467 --> 07:36.503
AND YOU STARTING TO WORK
ON MY NERVES.

07:36.503 --> 07:38.805
THANK YOU. COME ON.

07:38.805 --> 07:41.842
[ CHUCKLES ]

07:41.842 --> 07:43.644
[ SIGHS ]

07:43.644 --> 07:46.379
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

07:50.517 --> 07:53.854
WELL? WHAT DO YOU
GENTLEMEN THINK?

07:53.854 --> 07:57.023
VERY NICE.

07:57.023 --> 07:58.959
HUMBLE BEGINNINGS.

07:58.959 --> 08:00.561
YES.

08:00.561 --> 08:02.936
BUT NICE NONETHELESS.

08:02.936 --> 08:05.939
HOW ABOUT YOU, JIM?

08:07.007 --> 08:08.208
WHAT DO YOU THINK?

08:08.208 --> 08:10.343
I THINK
IT'S ‐‐ IT'S WONDERFUL.

08:10.343 --> 08:13.780
GOOD.
GLAD IT MEETS YOUR APPROVAL.

08:13.780 --> 08:14.815
IT DOES.

08:14.815 --> 08:16.282
VERY NICE.

08:16.282 --> 08:17.684
GOOD JOB.

08:17.684 --> 08:19.185
HMM.
GREAT.

08:21.688 --> 08:24.558
TELL ME SOMETHING. WHERE ‐‐
WHERE DID YOU GET THE STAFF?

08:24.558 --> 08:26.159
THEY'RE ALL VOLUNTEERS.

08:26.159 --> 08:27.293
REALLY?

08:27.293 --> 08:28.328
HMM.

08:28.328 --> 08:29.362
HUH.

08:29.362 --> 08:30.897
YEAH, REALLY,
THIS IS JUST A HANDFUL.

08:30.897 --> 08:32.566
THE REST ALL START

08:32.566 --> 08:34.735
ONCE WE GET THIS CAMPAIGN
UP AND RUNNING FULL SPEED.

08:34.735 --> 08:38.471
WELL,
THIS IS A FINE START.

08:38.471 --> 08:40.774
YES, IT IS.

08:40.774 --> 08:43.009
AND, YOU KNOW,
MY STAFF JUST GOT INTO TOWN.

08:43.009 --> 08:44.177
REALLY?
HMM.

08:44.177 --> 08:46.312
THEY'RE THE OIL
THAT MAKES IT ALL WORTHWHILE.

08:46.312 --> 08:48.915
I'M SURE THEY ARE.

08:48.915 --> 08:52.553
AND THEY'RE
THE WATCHDOGS.

08:52.553 --> 08:54.354
HMM.

08:54.354 --> 08:55.656
HMM.

08:55.656 --> 08:58.258
WOULD YOU LIKE TO SEE
YOUR OFFICE, JIM?

08:58.258 --> 08:59.993
I WOULD LOVE TO.

08:59.993 --> 09:01.502
GREAT.

09:01.502 --> 09:03.236
LEAD THE WAY.

09:07.207 --> 09:08.642
WOW.

09:10.176 --> 09:12.245
THIS IS NICE.
HMM.

09:12.245 --> 09:13.446
YES, IT IS.

09:13.446 --> 09:15.616
DAVID, WOULD YOU MIND
CLOSING THE DOOR?

09:15.616 --> 09:17.183
OH.

09:18.885 --> 09:21.121
LET ME MAKE THIS CLEAR
TO YOU, GENTLEMEN.

09:21.121 --> 09:24.390
EVERY SINGLE ONE OF THOSE YOUNG
LADIES IS OFF LIMITS TO YOU TWO.

09:24.390 --> 09:26.292
DO YOU UNDERSTAND?
MAGGIE.

09:26.292 --> 09:28.094
OH, WHAT, JIM?
DON'T GIVE ME THAT LOOK.

09:28.094 --> 09:30.230
YOUR REPUTATION
FAR PRECEDES YOU AT THIS POINT.

09:30.230 --> 09:32.398
MAGGIE.
WHAT? YOU WANT TO LIE TO ME?

09:32.398 --> 09:33.634
