ON THE WRONG FOOT?

09:35.235 --> 09:38.905
MAGGIE ‐‐
DAVID, I WASN'T SPEAKING TO YOU.

09:38.905 --> 09:40.907
ALTHOUGH THAT'S A GOOD POINT ‐‐
THE LIEUTENANT GOVERNOR

09:40.907 --> 09:42.509
SHOULD ALWAYS HAVE THE BACK
OF THE GOVERNOR.

09:45.378 --> 09:47.548
JIM...

09:47.548 --> 09:48.782
ANSWER ME.

09:48.782 --> 09:51.051
WHAT EXACTLY IS IT
YOU'D LIKE TO KNOW?

09:51.051 --> 09:53.453
I'LL GET TO THE QUESTION AT HAND
IN A MOMENT.

09:53.453 --> 09:56.356
BUT FIRST I WANT TO KNOW
THAT YOU UNDERSTOOD WHAT I SAID,

09:56.356 --> 09:58.792
THAT ALL OF THOSE YOUNG LADIES
ARE OFF LIMITS.

09:58.792 --> 10:02.235
YES.
OF COURSE I UNDERSTAND.

10:02.235 --> 10:04.437
GOOD. DAVID?

10:04.437 --> 10:07.207
YES.
BY ALL MEANS.

10:07.207 --> 10:08.809
I'M SURPRISED AT YOU,
MAGGIE.

10:08.809 --> 10:11.011
