ONLY DEALT IN FACTS.

10:14.715 --> 10:16.482
OKAY, YOU KNOW,
STOP RIGHT THERE, JIM.

10:16.482 --> 10:18.351
I DEAL IN ALL OF IT ‐‐
FACTS, RUMORS.

10:18.351 --> 10:21.454
THE TRUTH IS ALWAYS
SOMEWHERE IN BETWEEN.

10:21.454 --> 10:24.257
HMM.

10:24.257 --> 10:26.593
HMM.

10:26.593 --> 10:28.328
OKAY. [ CLEARS THROAT ]

10:28.328 --> 10:30.363
GOOD. SO...

10:30.363 --> 10:33.199
WHO'S CANDACE YOUNG?

10:35.401 --> 10:38.004
[ SIGHS ]
SILENCE, JIM. COME ON.

10:41.141 --> 10:43.644
CANDACE YOUNG IS THE DAUGHTER
OF MY HOUSEKEEPER. SO WHAT?

10:43.644 --> 10:46.212
OKAY.
DID YOU SLEEP WITH HER?

10:47.247 --> 10:48.248
MAGGIE.

10:48.248 --> 10:50.116
IT'S A "YES" OR "NO"
ANSWER.

10:50.116 --> 10:51.618
